22:50.336 --> 22:52.238 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of the LIGO Laboratory.

22:52.338 --> 22:56.809 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, that was a rudimentary
attempt at explaining
