the connection
to space-time?

23:57.303 --> 23:59.104 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
DAVE REITZE: Yes.

23:59.204 --> 24:02.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Does time and
space bend?
