or change
in light.

25:32.765 --> 25:34.166 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
DAVE REITZE: Yes.

25:34.266 --> 25:35.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: What does that
